The paper deals with deep reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI). The focus is on stability and efficiency, which are important considerations in robotics and control (cs.RO, cs.SY). The authors also validate their approach on the Atari benchmark, which involves computer vision and image processing (cs.CV).
